## Phase 1: Repository Index Construction — COMPLETED

- **Method:** Direct source file reading via shell commands (wsl bash -c cat)
- **Backend files fully read:** main.py, config.py, database.py, task_manager.py, llm_service.py, logger.py, all routers, all models, all services, all dependencies, all analyzer files, all RIM files, intelligence pipeline
