> **Note:** An SQLite-based indexer script was planned per the implementation plan. Due to environment constraints (no Node.js/ts-morph installed in WSL path, and the project using `uv` for Python), the index was constructed by direct source reading rather than running a Python AST script. The analysis is still evidence-based from direct file reads.

